                    "value": "<p>A dig-widget's face consists of a set of @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Thieves' Toolkit (Infiltrator)]{Infiltrator Thieves' Tools}. They can be salvaged from a destroyed dig-widget with a successful @Check[type:crafting|dc:20|name:Salvage Infiltration Tools] check. On a failed check, the tools are destroyed.</p>"
